Error: Error: "The Server Crashes After A Certain Amount Of Time And A "Java.Lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java Heap Space" Error Is Displayed."

Solution: 1. Log in to your Pterodactyl panel, and choose your server from the list of available servers.

2. Click on the "File Manager" section.

3. Navigate to the root directory of your server, and locate the "start.sh" script.

